name: 白糖糕 Baitanggao/ Some sort of style lora
description:
为什么叫白糖糕呢？因为它扎实朴素、香甜醇厚~

Eng description below. 更多例图下面相册请~

为什么上面例图显示inpaint：我用了Tiled Diffusion, 也就是 Multidiffusion 插件来upscale，主要就是会让图片更好看，你可以用常规方式upscale，当然也可以用txt2img产图。

原版未经MD：https://civitai.com/posts/136259

Feel free to merge this lora into lora/models/anything else that I don't know (if only you aren't trying to make money from it of course). 如想与其他lora/模型等混合，只要不盈利——敬请随意。

Reason why the sample images displayed as inpainting: I'm using the Tiled Diffusion, aka Multidiffusion plugin to upscale, you can of course generate with txt2img——myself did that, and sent the outcome to img2img, then upscaled it lel.

Original txt2img generates https://civitai.com/posts/136259

推荐CFG：如果没有Dynamic Thresholding就7，但是我强烈推荐Dynamic Thresholding插件，开20CFG，所有东西都好看一万倍（？

推荐分辨率：啥·都·行·呀，图里你们也看见了啥分辨率都有，就没不行的（草

推荐模型：我是在based64mix、holokukiv2.2上测试的，不过AOM3也不是不行，其他的自己试试也好啦。

Recommended CFG: 7 without Dynamic Thresholding Plugin, 14-20 with Dynamic Thresholding.

Recommended resolution: literally anything has been successful on my end, you can see it in the preview pics lel.

Recommended model: I've tested on based64mix、holokukiv2.2, however, AOM3、somethingv2_2 could also produce some nice things, feel free to test on other models!
